Laura La Varnie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laura_La_Varnie 0 Laura La Varnie (March 2, 1853 – September 18, 1939) was an American actress of the silent era. She appeared in 81 films between 1913 and 1930. She was born in Jefferson City, Missouri and died in Los Angeles, California.
